==Technical Overview==
Secret of Mana uses a HiROM memory mapping with 64 banks of ROM data. The game features:
* Real-time action combat system
* Ring menu interface
* 3-player cooperative multiplayer
* 8 Mana spirits with elemental magic
* 8 weapon types with charge attacks

