==Characters==
The game features three playable characters:

===The Hero (Randi)===
A young boy who accidentally releases the power of Mana and must restore it.

===The Girl (Primm)===
A young woman searching for her lost love Dyluck.

===The Sprite (Popoi)===
A mischievous sprite child who has lost their memory.

